Given that this appears to be isolated to a single user, the issue is more likely related to client-side factors rather than a systemic directory services problem. Potential contributing variables may include network connectivity at startup, Group Policy processing, profile loading, wireless negotiation, or other environmental conditions present at the time of logon.

